        Parameters:
        initFile - TG server init config file
        forceCreation - Force creation. Delete all the data in the db directory first.
        timeout - Number of milliseconds allowed to initialize the server
        Returns:
        the output stream of init operation
        Throws:
        TGInitException - Init operation fails or timeout occurs

      • killAll

        public static void killAll()
                    throws java.lang.Exception
         Kill all the TG server processes.
 Note that this method blindly tries to kill all the servers of the machine 
 and do not update the running status of those servers.
 - taskkill on Windows.
 - kill -9 on Unix.
        Throws:
        java.lang.Exception - Kill operation fails
